WEBVTT

00:00:31.038 --> 00:00:34.284
Dok ne podignemo granicu za
kriminalnu odgovornost na 18 godina,

00:00:34.284 --> 00:00:37.535
moramo se skoncentrirati na 
mijenjanje dnevne rutine ovih mladih.

00:00:38.155 --> 00:00:39.729
Znam to iz prve ruke.

00:00:40.329 --> 00:00:41.908
Prije no što sam napunio 18,

00:00:41.908 --> 00:00:45.855
proveo sam 400-tinjak dana 
na Rikers Islandu,

00:00:45.855 --> 00:00:46.769
usto

00:00:46.769 --> 00:00:49.973
proveo sam skoro tristo dana u samici

00:00:50.963 --> 00:00:52.440
i reći ću vam ovo:

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:56.768
Kad vrištiš iz sveg glasa na vrata samice

00:00:56.768 --> 00:00:59.345
ili vrištiš iz sveg glasa kroz prozor,

00:00:59.345 --> 00:01:01.267
umoriš se.